<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Deployment Latencies>
We are investigating increased deployment latencies in the EU-WEST-1 Region.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased Deployment Latencies>
Between 7:27 AM and 9:56 AM PDT we experienced increased deployment latencies in the EU-WEST-1 Region. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Informational message: Increased Error Rates and Latencies>
We can confirm increased error rates and latencies for the SSO service in the US-EAST-1 Region and continue to work towards resolution.

<http://status.aws.amazon.com/|Service is operating normally: [RESOLVED] Increased Error Rates and Latencies>
Between 10:30 AM and 2:18 PM PDT we experienced increased error rates and latencies for the SSO service in the US-EAST-1 Region. The issue has been resolved and the service is operating normally.
